        <mxCell id="RErO1YYLpNplc3-ivWxT-1" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Desejo:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Separo as minhas tasks em sessões&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- peço para ela elaborar uma task do jira&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- MCP do Jira busca a tarefa&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;-------------------&amp;nbsp; IA ------------------------&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- monta plano da task&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- dev aprova o planejamento&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- ia elabora a task&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- executa a task de acordo com o workflow fluxo-de-feature.md&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- commit na branch&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;worktree&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;em cada sessao&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;-------------------&amp;nbsp; IA ------------------------&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;dev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;revisa o conteudo da branch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;dev aceita as mudanças&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;workflow comita na branch worktree e nuvem&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;workflow passa a tarefa do jira para coluna &quot;teste&quot;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;QA testa&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;QA comita a branch q o fluxo de desenvolvimento definir&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=#36393d;fillColor=#cdeb8b;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
